data.value: Please do not adjust the recognition interval at will. If the recognition interval is too small, it may lead to the recognition of the wrong intermediate situation. If the game connected is a game with a short animation time such as JJ Chess, the number of recognition confirmations can be adjusted to . If the game connected is a game with a long animation time such as Tiantian Chess, the number of recognition confirmations must be at least twice.
